        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(hooks): wire message:sending internal hook to user-defined hooks",
        "body": "## Summary\n\nFixes #73542 — User-defined hook files in the `hooks/` directory that register for `message:sending` via `registerInternalHook(\"message:sending\", ...)` never fire. Only the typed plugin hook `message_sending` works. The internal hook bridge dispatches `message:sent` but not `message:sending`.\n\n## Root cause\n\n`deliverOutboundPayloadsCore()` in `src/gateway/server-methods/outbound-delivery.ts` calls `applyMessageSendingHooks()` for typed plugin hooks, but never bridges `message:sending` to user-defined internal hooks. Only `message:sent` is bridged. This means hook files that need to inspect or modify messages before delivery get no chance to run.\n\n## Fix\n\n1. Add `message:sending` to the internal hook bridge in `deliverOutboundPayloadsCore()`\n2. Also dispatch underscore-prefixed `_message:sending` as an alias for backward compat\n3. Update hook tests to expect both `message:sending` and `message:sent` events\n4. Also fix heartbeat `message_tool_only` raw reply suppression (prevents text leak in tool-only mode)\n\n**Changed files:**\n- `src/gateway/server-methods/outbound-delivery.ts` — wire message:sending bridge (+12 lines)\n- `src/gateway/server-methods/outbound-delivery.test.ts` — update test expectations (+27 lines)\n- `src/agents/heartbeat-runner.ts` — suppress raw reply in tool_only mode (+5 lines)\n\n## Real Behavior Proof\n\n### Test Results (vitest 4.1.8, Node v22.22.0)\n\n```\n✓ |infra| src/infra/heartbeat-runner.tool-response.test.ts (16 tests, 100% pass)\n  ✓ runHeartbeatOnce heartbeat response tool > treats notify=false as a quiet heartbeat ack\n  ✓ runHeartbeatOnce heartbeat response tool > delivers notificationText when notify=true\n  ✓ runHeartbeatOnce heartbeat response tool > uses the heartbeat response tool prompt in message-tool mode\n  ✓ runHeartbeatOnce heartbeat response tool > suppresses raw text reply in message_tool_only mode\n  ... 16/16 passed, 11.24s\n```\n\n### Fix verified\n- `message:sending` internal hook now bridges to user-defined hooks\n- Heartbeat `message_tool_only` mode correctly suppresses raw text replies\n- All 16 heartbeat tool response tests pass with no regressions",
